###############
## KCALS.NET ##
###############
## ENCODING ##
Options -Indexes
SetEnv TZ America/Sao_Paulo
AddDefaultCharset UTF-8

## COMPRESS ##
AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE text/html text/javascript text/css text/xml text/plain font/ttf application/font-woff text/cache-manifest application/x-web-app-manifest+json

## NO CACHE ##
<ifModule mod_headers.c>
	Header unset ETag
	Header add Access-Control-Allow-Origin "*"
	<filesMatch "\.(php|js|css|ttf|cur|ico|png|appcache|json|webapp|txt|db)$">
		Header set Cache-Control "max-age=0, no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate"
		Header set Pragma "no-cache"
		Header set Expires "Fri, 19 Feb 1982 05:00:00 GMT"
	</filesMatch>
</ifModule>

## MIME ##
AddType font/ttf .ttf
AddType application/font-woff .woff
AddType application/x-web-app-manifest+json .webapp
AddType text/cache-manifest .manifest
AddType text/cache-manifest .appcache
AddType text/plain .db

